        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on proofs [of <hi rend="italic">Principles of geology</hi>, 10th ed. (1867–8)]: CL does not allude to the specialisation of classes.</p> 
            <p>Discusses CL’s argument from the absence of Cetacea in Secondary rocks;</p>
            <p>finds his discussion of man "superfluous and too orthodox".</p>
